deck: Christophe Coronas, who publishes under the name Cecil, is a comic book artist from Bordeaux. After his studies in fine arts, Cécil worked a librarian, graphic artist and illustrator. His debut comic 'L'Empreinte des Chimères' was created under his real name Coronas, and was published by Vents d'Ouest in 1990. In 1999, he started the series 'Le Réseau Bombyce' with Eric Corbeyran at Les Humanoïdes Associés. The third and final book was published in 2010.
